The '''Sith Arts Academy''' was a [[Sith academy]] established on [[Thule/Legends|Thule]] sometime prior to the [[Battle of Naboo/Legends|Battle of Naboo]], and presumably before the [[Seventh Battle of Ruusan]]. The fallen [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] [[Drevveka Hoctu]] was once its [[Headmaster/Legends|headmaster]].<ref name="Geonosis">''[[Geonosis and the Outer Rim Worlds]]''</ref>

